{"text": "The run was a success because the agent first inspected the repository and key scripts, created the expected results subdirectories, ran the project pipeline to completion, and finally wrote an answer file with the requested values.[T0B2][T0B5][T0B14][T0B61][T0B88:<RANGE>{
