}</RANGE>][T0B89:<RANGE>Wrote file successfully.</RANGE>] The main non-trivial obstacle was dependency setup: R was initially unavailable, the first package installation attempt failed because the site library was not writable, and a bulk installation later timed out.[T0B21:<RANGE>/usr/bin/bash: line 1: Rscript: command not found</RANGE>][T0B31:<RANGE>'lib = "/usr/local/lib/R/site-library"' is not writable</RANGE>][T0B33:<RANGE>bash tool terminated command after exceeding timeout 600000 ms.</RANGE>] The agent recovered by installing R system-wide, verifying that Rscript was present, then switching to sudo-backed installs and installing the missing packages individually until a final check showed none were missing.[T0B24][T0B27:<RANGE>/usr/bin/Rscript
Rscript (R) version 4.3.3 (2024-02-29)</RANGE>][T0B40][T0B42][T0B44][T0B46][T0B48][T0B50][T0B53:<RANGE>Missing packages:  </RANGE>] Its overall strategy used multiple distinct workflows rather than just one straight path: repository reading, environment repair with apt and R package installation, pipeline execution with the master script, and answer extraction through both standalone R calculations and HTML/figure inspection.[T0B0][T0B24][T0B56][T0B61][T0B68][T0B76][T0B80] During extraction it hit a smaller path issue when a standalone R snippet pointed to the wrong location for data_typofixes.csv, but it checked the actual file layout and reran the calculation with the correct path.[T0B65:<RANGE>Error: No such file: ../../data/03_analyses/data_typofixes.csv</RANGE>][T0B67][T0B84][T0B85] Because those issues were resolved, master_script.R generated the cleaned results outputs, the agent verified that Table 1 listed 255 Included Articles in After.OS and that the Pre-RC analysis-script not-available percentage was 100, and then saved those answers to answer.json, which makes the successful outcome reasonable.[T0B61][T0B77:<RANGE>Included Articles | 519 | 264 | 255</RANGE>][T0B69][T0B88][T0B89]", "citations": [{"target": {"item": {"block_idx": 2, "item_type": "block_content", "content_idx": null, "agent_run_id": "8b32c065-55e1-4f67-a047-f3b30495b0f4", "collection_id": "", "transcript_id": "09c6a7ad-eabb-4838-8b4c-a9b8a42e2a5b"}, "text_range": null}, "end_idx": 238, "start_idx": 232}, {"target": {"item": {"block_idx": 5, "item_type": "block_content", "content_idx": null, "agent_run_id": "8b32c065-55e1-4f67-a047-f3b30495b0f4", "collection_id": "", "transcript_id": "09c6a7ad-eabb-4838-8b4c-a9b8a42e2a5b"}, "text_range": null}, "end_idx": 244, "start_idx": 238}, {"target": {"item": {"block_idx": 14, "item_type": "block_content", "content_idx": null, "agent_run_id": "8b32c065-55e1-4f67-a047-f3b30495b0f4", "collection_id": "", "transcript_id": "09c6a7ad-eabb-4838-8b4c-a9b8a42